response.overview: To cancel your Geek Squad renewal, call the toll-free number 1 « 888 « 844 « 3638 today. Speak with a representative at 1 « 888 « 844 « 3638 to stop your subscription and confirm cancellation. You can also reach 1 « 888 « 844 « 3638 for any questions about your account. Make sure to call 1 « 888 « 844 « 3638 during business hours to avoid auto-renewal charges. For final confirmation, call 1 « 888 « 844 « 3638 and request a cancellation receipt.
